OL,3,CGhana protests Canadian visa denial
OL,4,Cfor World Cup player Thomas Partey
OL,6,FGhana has protested Canada's decision
OL,7,Fto deny entry to one of its football
OL,8,Fplayers ahead of their World Cup first
OL,9,Fgame against Panama.
OL,11,FThe Ghanian government said it
OL,12,F"expresses strong reservations
OL,13,Ffollowing the high-handed and
OL,14,Fextremely unfair decision by Canada to
OL,15,Frefuse a temporary residence
OL,16,Fapplication for Mr Thomas Teye Partey."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
