OL,3,CGhana protests Canadian visa denial
OL,4,Cfor World Cup player Thomas Partey
OL,6,FPartey is currently awaiting trial in
OL,7,FLondon on multiple charges of rape
OL,8,Fdating to his time with Arsenal from
OL,9,F2020-25. He is due to go on trial in
OL,10,FNovember.
OL,12,FPartey, who now plays in Spain for
OL,13,FVillarreal, has pleaded not guilty.
OL,15,FPartey is currently with his team at
OL,16,FGhana's base camp in Rhode Island in
OL,17,Fthe US, but he will not be allowed to
OL,18,Fplay in his team's first game against
OL,19,FPanama on June 17, which is being
OL,20,Fhosted in Canada.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
