OL,3,CGhana protests Canadian visa denial
OL,4,Cfor World Cup player Thomas Partey
OL,6,FThe 2026 World Cup is split between
OL,7,FCanada, the US and Mexico.
OL,9,FImmigration, Refugees and Citizenship
OL,10,FCanada said in a statement that every
OL,11,Fperson wanting to come to Canada is
OL,12,Fassessed individually "based on the
OL,13,Ffacts available and the law that
OL,14,Fapplies."
