OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781444876
OL,3,CGhana protests Canadian visa denial
OL,4,Cfor World Cup player Thomas Partey
OL,6,F"Canada is proud to be a host country
OL,7,Ffor the 2026 FIFA World Cup and is
OL,8,Fworking to facilitate a successful
OL,9,Fevent while maintaining the safety and
OL,10,Fsecurity of Canadians," the IRCC said
OL,11,Fin the statement. "Canada has been
OL,12,Fconsistent that hosting major events
OL,13,Fdoes not change Canada's immigration
OL,14,Flaws."
OL,16,FHe will be able to play June 23 when
OL,17,FGhana plays England in Foxborough,
OL,18,FMassachusetts. Ghana concludes group
OL,19,Fplay June 27 against Croatia in
OL,20,FPhiladelphia.
